## Detection Value

| Event | Security Value |
|-------|---------------|
| `ERROR` in server.log | Pipeline failure — investigate immediately |
| `WARN` repeated | Degraded performance — monitor |
| Input stopped | MikroTik logs no longer arriving |
| Auth failure to UI | Unauthorized access attempt to Graylog |

